{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">About This Game</h2><br>Embark on a serene journey through the musical realms of Chromatic Isle, a short 30-minute low-poly 3D puzzle game intended to be completed in one sitting. Explore four distinct areas, each themed around a different season and offering a unique music-focused puzzle. Unwind and let the music guide your way.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features</h2><br>\ud83c\udf31 <strong>Winter, Spring, Summer, Autumn</strong>: Traverse through four enchanting seasons, each with its own distinct charm and puzzle inspired by the season's theme.<br> <br>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684780/extras/Chromatic_Isle_Seasons_Gif.gif?t=1705327435\" /><br><br>\ud83c\udfb5 <strong>Harmonious Puzzles</strong>: Engage in a variety of music-centric puzzles that immerse you in the melodic ambiance of Chromatic Isle.<br><br>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684780/extras/Chromatic_Isle_Puzzles_Gif.gif?t=1705327435\" /><br><br>\ud83d\uddfa\ufe0f <strong>Non-Linear Design</strong>: Enjoy the freedom to roam and choose your own path, creating a non-linear adventure tailored to your preferences.<br><br>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684780/extras/Chromatic_Isle_NonLinear_Gif.gif?t=1705327435\" /><br><br>\ud83c\udfa8 <strong>Low-Poly Aesthetics</strong>: The island's tranquil low-poly visuals provide a serene backdrop to your non-linear journey.<br><br>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.